    • Field Detail

      • sheetName

        private java.lang.String sheetName
        The sheetName variable holds the name of the current sheet, for example: "New sheet...".

      • cells

        final java.util.Map<Sheet.Position,Cell> cells
        The cells HashMap binds Position instances to Cell instances. A Position holds a unique column and row index.

      • columnCount

        private int columnCount
        The amount of columns used in this sheet. This is used to limit the amount of values returned by methods that return cell ranges. This value automatically increments when a Cell is inserted with a higher column index.

      • rowCount

        private int rowCount
        The amount of rows used in this sheet. This is used to limit the amount of values returned by methods that return cell ranges. This value automatically increments when a Cell is inserted with a higher row index.

      • stable

        private STable stable
